1. *Duha* je izgubila pravac. (The spirit has lost its way.)
2. U *duhu* je zakona vladalo puno razumevanja. (In the spirit of the law, there was a lot of understanding.)
3. Ona je prepoznala njegovu *dušu*. (She recognised his soul.)
4. Ona je došla u *duhu* da podrži njegovu ideju. (She came in spirit to support his idea.)
5. Svaki čovek poseduje svoju *dušu*. (Every man has his own soul.)